    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Additive color screen plates introduced by Agfa Company on the German market in 1916. There are four generations of this additive color screen process on plate: Agfa Farbenplatte (1916-1923), Neue Agfa Farbenplatte (1923-1932), Agfacolor-Platte (1932-1938) and Agfacolor Ultra (1936-1938).</Note_Text>
